;SEQUENCE
AUTHORS INFORMED THAT THE SEQUENCE OF 
CHICKEN TALIN IS NOT AVAILABLE IN ANY
REFERENCE DATABASE. THE SEQUENCE HAS 
BEEN DESCRIBED IN THE PUBLICATION:

HEMMINGS, L., REES, D.J.G., OHANIAN, V.,
BOLTON, S.J., GILMORE, A.P., PATEL, N., 
PRIDDLE, H., TREVITHICK, J.E., HYNES, 
R.O., & CRITCHLEY, D.R. (1996). TALIN 
CONTAINS THREE ACTIN-BINDING SITES EACH 
OF WHICH IS ADJACENT TO A VINCULIN-BINDING 
SITE. J. CELL SCI., 109, 2715-2726.
;
